snippet.textDisplay:
I discovered this situation while I was thinking about adopting a cat, since I have another cat who is really social, extra space and lots of love to give. Cloud's story came up, a beautiful one eyed boy abandoned to die in the streets in UAE...His story can be seen here: https://m.facebook.com/groups/2882118798479755?view=permalink&id=3749239815100978

The relocation cost is 525 pounds total, which is more than I was ready to pay for initially, but I simply cannot ignore him.

Now, I am trying to raise funds to help me with the cost, so if you could help by sharing or donating please do ♡ https://www.justgiving.com/crowdfunding/cloud-will-go-home…

Thank you very much!
